full_text:
GENERAL.

91.5.201.4. Terms Not Defined.  The definitions in Webster’s Third New California Dictionary of the English Language, Unabridged, shall be considered as providing ordinarily accepted meanings.
plain_text:
LOS ANGELES MUNICIPAL CODE

GENERAL. (§ 91.5.201)

  GENERAL.91.5.201.4. Terms Not Defined.  The definitions in Webster’s Third
New California Dictionary of the English Language, Unabridged, shall be
considered as providing ordinarily accepted meanings.
